high_descs: Turn around to walk to the long brown couch.
Pick up the keys from the middle of the couch.
Turn around to face the ottoman.
Put the keys down on the ottoman.
Walk to the right section of the long brown couch.
Pick up the other keys from the right side of the long brown couch.
Turn around to face the ottoman.
Set the other keys down next to the keys on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Move two sets of keys to the ottoman.

high_descs: Go right and then right again to face the couch with the computer on it.
Pick the keys up from the couch.
Turn around and face the ottoman in front of the couch.
Put the keys on the ottoman.
Turn to face the other set of keys on the couch.
Pick the keys up from the couch.
Turn left and then left again and turn to face the ottoman.
Put the keys down on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Put two sets of keys on an ottoman.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the middle of the dresser on your left, and turn right to walk to the long sofa with the white pillow.
Pick up the set of keys close to the pillow on the sofa.
Turn left, walk to the wall, turn left, take a step forward, and turn left towards the ottoman.
Place the set of keys next to the laptop on the ottoman.
Turn left, take a step forward, and then turn right towards the laptop on the sofa.
Pick up the set of keys to the right of the laptop on the sofa.
Turn left, walk to the wall, turn left, take a step forward, and turn left towards the ottoman.
Place the set of keys next to the other set on the ottoman.
anns.task_desc: Place the two set of keys on the long sofa to the ottoman.
